webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) Sudden but unique view from Lköpping. The New Street seen to the east. A little beyond the man on the street, the Läroverksgatan runs from the left and Djurgårdsgatan from the right. In the White House on the Right, Maria Teschs ran her photo business between 1873-1917 - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMEA0001240015. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021017436624. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
